SENTINEL memory specs
---------------------

The SENTINEL is equipped with 64 or 128 KiB of RAM and 4 KiB of ROM.
Only the low 64 KiB of an 128 KiB chip are used in R0.

Please note that only SRAM chips that provide both a /CS1 and a CS2 pin can be
used. Chips without a CS2 pin cannot be used with this setup.

Bill of materials:
- 64 KiB or 128 KiB SRAM
- 4 KiB UVEPROM or EEPROM (2732 or compatible)
- 74HC32 quad 2-input OR gates
- 1x DIP-14 socket (optional)
- 1x DIP-24 socket (optional)
- 1x DIP-32 socket (optional)
- 3x capacitor 100 nF

